{"tid":667459,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"ALBION ONLINE 有冇人玩","createTime":"2018-05-16T19:02:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-24T02:42:15.000Z","uid":185884,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"2e3c42838204638fb4140085831d6d53d2b908fe","tid":667459,"uid":185884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T19:02:54.000Z","msg":"如題"},{"pid":"8455b6f95f0948021bfe22de142e28ff3d5bb062","tid":667459,"uid":185884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e3c42838204638fb4140085831d6d53d2b908fe","tid":667459,"uid":185884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T19:02:54.000Z","msg":"如題"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T05:24:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3c504e4a33b1f21087ec217b312d2d4292c5f4fc","tid":667459,"uid":180348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T05:31:33.000Z","msg":"我係最早果批玩家黎<br />\n不過太垃圾一個月就quit左"},{"pid":"a99df284193c51722fe26c706912133c47f6c25a","tid":667459,"uid":180561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T05:40:06.000Z","msg":"玩緊"},{"pid":"f4b41d79cdb8d55d1784cb69e68453efe0af457f","tid":667459,"uid":185884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c504e4a33b1f21087ec217b312d2d4292c5f4fc","tid":667459,"uid":180348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T05:31:33.000Z","msg":"我係最早果批玩家黎<br />\n不過太垃圾一個月就quit左"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T06:38:58.000Z","msg":"有冇其他推介?"},{"pid":"67087fc56bdb02870eaa86d2eedcf65dc40a35b3","tid":667459,"uid":17123,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T07:13:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">買之前睇咗先</span></span><br />\n<br />\n勸世文: <br />\n<br />\n近日Albion Online係Steam到上架 <br />\n<br />\n相信好多人會因為比佢濃厚嘅UO元素所吸引到 <br />\n<br />\n的而且確 隻Game有好多地方好類近UO <br />\n<br />\n玩家自主嘅經濟系統 豐富嘅採集系統 公會系統 地下城系統etc.<br />\n<br />\n但係同時間 Albion亦有好多問題會令到新舊玩家心灰意冷 以至係棄坑同卻步<br />\n<br />\n最令人髮指嘅係 隻Game內建嘅Gold系統同VIP系統 <br />\n<br />\nGold相等於而家手機game嘅課金 佢可以兌換做遊戲入而嘅貨幣同延長VIP時間 但係只可以通過課金入手或者玩家之間通過Gold市場去兌換 <br />\n<br />\n而Gold市場嘅兌換率係根據玩家嘅需求同供應 反映出嚟 由於課金嘅人小 而買金兌換VIP嘅人多 金價由開Server到而家一年期間有升冇跌<br />\n<br />\n而冇咗VIP個後果係 你係隻game無論做咩效率都會低一半 本身隻game已經好Grind需要大量時間去farm 有VIP先叫做接近正常速度<br />\n<br />\n久而久之 後果就係成隻Game嘅經濟系統崩潰<br />\n<br />\n除此之外 仲有好多問題 例如: Server廢 (PvP區lag一lag 比人殺咗 就成身清空), 官方商城曾經ban過亞洲區IP, PvE難以生存, 官方將steam上架嘅成本轉移去新玩家到<br />\n<br />\n詳細啲可以去Steam評論/ Albion討論區研究"},{"pid":"8ac27a3b7e958b56d100bd5a5952361c453ff6f3","tid":667459,"uid":180348,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f4b41d79cdb8d55d1784cb69e68453efe0af457f","tid":667459,"uid":185884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c504e4a33b1f21087ec217b312d2d4292c5f4fc","tid":667459,"uid":180348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T05:31:33.000Z","msg":"我係最早果批玩家黎<br />\n不過太垃圾一個月就quit左"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T06:38:58.000Z","msg":"有冇其他推介?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T08:26:01.000Z","msg":"Ashes of creation, pantheon rise of the fallen<br />\n兩個都未出，都係大作，original idea, 唔係宜家果堆copy and paste mmorpgs"},{"pid":"25e1cd012d13ac59e364ef468501f9c56d11dc32","tid":667459,"uid":58120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ac27a3b7e958b56d100bd5a5952361c453ff6f3","tid":667459,"uid":180348,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f4b41d79cdb8d55d1784cb69e68453efe0af457f","tid":667459,"uid":185884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c504e4a33b1f21087ec217b312d2d4292c5f4fc","tid":667459,"uid":180348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T05:31:33.000Z","msg":"我係最早果批玩家黎<br />\n不過太垃圾一個月就quit左"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T06:38:58.000Z","msg":"有冇其他推介?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T08:26:01.000Z","msg":"Ashes of creation, pantheon rise of the fallen<br />\n兩個都未出，都係大作，original idea, 唔係宜家果堆copy and paste mmorpgs"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T08:46:49.000Z","msg":"同場加映Chronicles of Elyria"},{"pid":"d